  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description

    Interface for mapping key/parent fields on pojo entities.

    This is a wrapper for a Path that makes it backwards; instead of going from tail to head, it has links from head to tail.

    Utility that makes it easy to generate If conditions.
    Keys
    Holds static metadata about entity keys.

    NullProperty
    Property to use with translators when there isn't a relevant property; for example, when making a filterable or when creating translator for the root entity.
    Path

    Associates a Property with a Translator and provides a more convenient interface.
